name: DrainSounds
0:
”Alexa open drain sounds”
”Alexa ask drain sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: drain sounds
des:
Enhance sleep and focus with Drain sounds! Listen to the soft putter of rain drops building up and swirling into a drain. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Drain Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
